name: Goodlato Handcrafted Low Calorie Gelato
content: Goodlato launches our new product, "Ugly Sorbets" on 21st August, 11.30am - 2.30pm at @treatsure pop up at their concept store! Now listen! Approximately 20% of produce or more gets thrown out for cosmetic reasons like weird shapes, odd colors, or blemishes. To fight against unnecessary food waste, we partnered with treatsure to source these "ugly" berries to turn into tasty and refreshing sorbets, in Goodlato style. Because not only are we committed to sustainability, we are also committed to making our products low in calorie and low sugar for a health-driven cause, and this will always be in Goodlato's DNA. See you at the pop up event! Find out more about this event on @treatsure #treatsuresg #goodlato #lowcalorie #sustainable #produce #sustainablesg

In celebration of this new menu launch, we‚Äôll be having 50% off our L bowl from 16th to 30th May, in-store only!

name: Goodlato Handcrafted Low Calorie Gelato
content: The wait is over! We‚Äôve been working really hard on this menu revamp. Goodlato started out 4 months ago, serving y‚Äôall artisanal low-calorie gelato that tastes equally decadent. Come December, we have decided to challenge ourselves further by ditching our plain-ole flavours and go all out with blasphemous & outrageous flavour creations. We love challenges, hence, we promised to make them all low-in-calorie, high in protein and do the ‚Äúimpossible‚Äù‚Ä¶ Ironic ain‚Äôt it? But that‚Äôs what makes it fun. Come visit us! We promise to fulfil your cheat day dreams. Our scoops go as low as 49kcal/scoop (Normal ice cream is about 200kcal/scoop).- Are you outrageously good or just plain ole boring?
